      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It's unlikely that your smart thermostat and fridge are directly reacting to your emotions, but there could be other factors at play. One possible explanation could be the presence of alternative radio frequency (RF) smart home devices or devices taking longer to update their information. It's worth checking your home for other devices that might be sending arbitrary temperature signals, or verifying that your smart thermostat and fridge are the only ones in the kitchen.",
